{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content-editor-core lake-engine lake-typography-classic\" data-lake-element=\"root\" data-selection-undefined=\"%7B%22path%22%3A%5B%5B86%2C1%2C0%2C44%5D%2C%5B86%2C1%2C0%2C44%5D%5D%2C%22active%22%3Atrue%7D\"><p data-lake-id=\"638d48d64dd68f0804f3da8e2d630c8a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"label\"><span class=\"lake-card-label-container\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 232, 230); color: rgb(130, 0, 20); opacity: 1; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 200px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; margin-bottom: -4px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; padding: 2px 5px; text-overflow: ellipsis; line-height: 14px; margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px;\" draggable=\"true\">workflowy</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"label\"><span class=\"lake-card-label-container\" style=\"background: rgb(255, 248, 189); color: rgb(97, 71, 0); opacity: 1; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 200px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; margin-bottom: -4px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; padding: 2px 5px; text-overflow: ellipsis; line-height: 14px; margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px;\" draggable=\"true\">看板</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"label\"><span class=\"lake-card-label-container\" style=\"background: rgb(228, 247, 210); color: rgb(19, 82, 0); opacity: 1; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 200px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; margin-bottom: -4px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; padding: 2px 5px; text-overflow: ellipsis; line-height: 14px; margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px;\" draggable=\"true\">web 应用</span></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"label\"><span class=\"lake-card-label-container\" style=\"background: rgb(233, 233, 233); color: rgb(89, 89, 89); opacity: 1; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 200px; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; margin-bottom: -4px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; padding: 2px 5px; text-overflow: ellipsis; line-height: 14px; margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px;\" draggable=\"true\">商业半免费</span></span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"85dffd7bd8e4ad38f3564a83f4fcd7ec\" id=\"SVT3t\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">何为分形看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"037a8d2b9396ce66a1ac160144131156\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"126f8dae1b6581bdb7ca1813c0c4fd43\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">workflowy 的大纲式数据本质上是以树状结构来组织的。</p><p data-lake-id=\"f76c4ac64fe056167703d02693f71e83\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"a83f6607b4b772d2809e5f54db52af17\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">如果想象出一个虚无的根节点，那么 workflowy 中的所有内容全部可以认为属于同一棵树，这棵树中的每一个节点(bullet)都是一棵子树，并且可以点击它直接聚焦到这棵子树。以前 workflowy 只有大纲这一种展示形式，聚焦到某一个节点之后，该节点和下属子节点也是以大纲列表的形式来展示的。</p><p data-lake-id=\"2dad5606c7cd820eea465f32d8f44f3d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"acf593137cc6db2e1279b5eb31a1597f\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><strong>树状的逻辑结构除了用大纲列表来展示，能不能有别的展示方式呢？</strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"e3006befd41930bd2e10d0285c18f625\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><strong><br></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ab001af2cd0ec3e2f079b2449f0e3901\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">对于这个问题，幕布就有一个非常成功、也可以说是非常失败的尝试，那就是从大纲列表生成思维导图。之所以说它成功，是因为这个功能成功取悦了大量普通用户。为什么说它失败呢，直接引用我以前对这个功能的评价：</p><p data-lake-id=\"89d2af8ca9a28b84c04555b6b2e90be4\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><blockquote style=\"padding-left: 1em; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); opacity: 0.6;\">从大纲生成思维导图的功能完全是鸡肋+自我陶醉，org-mode 也有导出思维导图的功能，我一次都没用过。说到底，生成一个全文字的“思维导图”到底要给谁看？如果是给别人看，那思维导图根本就不是一个适合分享的形式，如果谁发一坨思维导图长图片给我，除非这个人地位比我还高，否则我一眼都不会看；如果是给自己看，那就更没意义了，要是整篇大纲笔记内容很少，根本没必要平铺成思维导图，内容再稍微多一点呢，生成的思维导图根本没法用肉眼看，那种长得要上下翻页才能看的长图片早就违背了思维导图创始人东尼·博赞最强调的横向平铺原则，这种东西到底哪里好了？大纲类软件要想鸟瞰内容，真正需要的不是长图片，而是一套完善顺手的大纲快捷键、强大便捷的搜索过滤功能、多条件生成稀疏树功能。以幕布为首的大纲软件之所以会把生成思维导图作为卖点，还不是因为在这三大核心功能上面做得太差劲了。</blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"0ae4db3e2baffe7c3cbb7c52ed3814d1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c2f4c7adb5cd95339a9cdb15fb4d3256\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">树状结构有没有别的更有意义的展示方式呢？有，这就是 workflowy 新推出的分形看板(fractal boards)。</p><p data-lake-id=\"7d3e56b9b4e8c9f1ef9c9aaf995defa6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"2cebdc793ec3194a1feb5386511d29f1\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">现在，workflowy 新增了分形看板功能，<strong>整个 workflowy 中的每一个节点全部可以在 (bullets / board) 这两种显示模式之间切换。</strong>无论选择哪种显示模式，原始数据都不会有任何改变，改变的只是展示形式。如果选择 bullets 模式(也就是过去的列表模式)，一棵子树会以一个列表的形式展示，而如果选择 board 模式，一棵子树就会以一个看板的形式来展示。</p><h2 data-lake-id=\"3ec4a273ef4579394e3632f6e65fc152\" id=\"VpoPX\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">分形看板使用举例</h2><p data-lake-id=\"b51476553ebd68e07144571462f3c801\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"7571e28ed87277f3e4bb57242b5fb619\" id=\"Dxbqv\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">eg 1：将一个列表转化为看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"be5858445056e88b61530b12580d5cae\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"416e1b5166eb6cfb1e69b890aa099400\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">用一些直观的例子来展示一下分形看板功能。</p><p data-lake-id=\"86830bd1dc865ec9c6c8c183399810e8\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"13e71585424c8367f26f6b3a53921d90\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">这是 workflowy 中一个普通的列表：</p><p data-lake-id=\"bf01838c735a75f908e24e9fedce460e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"90f3c28688eb68f928e7e9505ea9a092\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327574674-945350ae-660c-404a-9a2c-d862ece6b2f1.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"209px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 202px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"614ee460ff07664f52b29d6f2422ae6e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"e0dc15b1d368cbf4de2dfacab162bf90\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">如果把 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">一号看板</code> 这个节点的展示方式从 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">bullets</code> 改为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">board</code>，</p><p data-lake-id=\"9ecf19e5c954df1f7a55e6bbdb5048ab\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"1e3e31d35fb48d372f7ce51224a44e80\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327643564-0a03ab2b-3e6b-4d9f-b8a7-2491c54a258f.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"137px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 261px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"d2b7612cafd547a706ccd408fb591b09\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"7806d3b7a8a4577da187760a9b35dba7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">整个列表就会以看板形式展示出来：</p><p data-lake-id=\"45b8746dab72a81fff7d0a55c0f2ae3e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"5c0b3fec9231b96840035875c3eccca3\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327722109-19668157-6bd0-4fa2-8022-a013af17ae82.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"221px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 732.5px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"714b67875930dcd088e1520363173c51\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ec9479a47e521381287943ed46adca14\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">未开始</code>、<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">进行中</code>、<code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">已完结</code> 这三个子节点原本都是 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">一号看板</code> 的一级子节点，它们现在变成了看板中的一个个竖排列表。</p><p data-lake-id=\"d9625c990deccae717128fd56f6cabe9\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ba8c89055ce97a3c2d23222d97c2151a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">任务 1</code> 和 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">任务 2</code> 原本是 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">未开始</code> 这个节点的一级子节点，它们现在变成了看板列表中的卡片。</p><p data-lake-id=\"bd1a683d7506dfdedfa3fcd538e52250\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"2330d6e6c99c22ae2208608793761c5c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">任务 1</code> 下面还有其它的内容，所以 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">任务 1</code> 这张卡片依然是一个列表，在这张卡片内部可以进行 workflowy 原有的各种大纲操作。</p><p data-lake-id=\"c89053ef299bdd76a0b34a661737c6e2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"4d90919482cb0ca74dc13da9cabdf1d6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">最重要的是，卡片拖拽、竖排列表拖拽等看板常用操作也是支持的，不过 UI 的拖拽手感比不上 trello 那么细致。(在 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">settings -&gt; experimental features</code> 当中开启 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">better interaction for cards boards</code> 之后有些许改善，但是不推荐开启)</p><h2 data-lake-id=\"bf34ecff26a4f8e761fa275e32c44f3e\" id=\"sFT3e\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">eg 2：平铺显示多个看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"9b913a6fe6af4ce4cf0de421ab597939\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"f1724a95f2f16583209e59654d0dbe6e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">从上一个例子可以看出 workflowy 是如何将一个节点及其下属内容转换为看板来展示的，即使不聚焦到该节点，在任何列表中把一个 board 节点展开，都可以得到一个看板视图。这也就是说，多个看板可以同时展示出来：</p><p data-lake-id=\"f71fcc41d88747ecae366341940a105c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"42021f2d8e6272d4f180cdbfea022f0f\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327787239-8484f6e4-6330-4630-b02a-251846f4244e.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"381px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 746.5px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"cce07631b15035c79444b005708eab2a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"53581d5b6a1284b6f4368d07b88cac6e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">同时平铺多个看板，trello 等传统看板工具是做不到的，而且分形看板还可以<strong>跨看板拖拽卡片</strong>。也就是说，二号看板中的卡片可以直接拖拽到一号看板中。</p><p data-lake-id=\"af9cd5ce611f6427a2a2d51b56b6d1f2\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"a8a50a189c21cab9ce25a44e2b3fe940\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">上面两点 notion 也可以做到，但还有一点是 notion 也做不到的，那就是分形看板的跨看板拖拽卡片不仅仅是针对卡片，还可以<strong>跨看板拖拽整个竖排列表</strong>，或是<strong>跨看板直接拖拽卡片内部的列表元素</strong>：</p><p data-lake-id=\"03ff959239fc4b878e421c6e91bb1a03\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"edecdf8bc22d7bb3086d9c7e1406d177\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327857986-9eed53f6-cd2d-4359-b421-12c0c26b7104.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"223px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 748.5px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"32f4ec19e07e06e35048ee6372607fe7\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ebe7de87d1c5437bd8bdcb7a543207b3\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">上图中用红框标出来的元素都可以直接跨看板拖拽。如果内容多到不方便用鼠标拖拽，还可以退回列表模式，用 workflowy 原有的方式来移动。在多看板联动这件事上，workflowy 的分形看板已经无敌了。</p><h2 data-lake-id=\"4bc9caa169c4159445fea56ba5e30946\" id=\"MRifH\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">eg 3：无限嵌套的分形看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"996967aa428895176480ebabd9868152\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">先看看前面的一号看板：</p><p data-lake-id=\"904296a16ab8c28cdc9fe4588a0796e9\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"06ac3269f9e5ac779ffead7181436b2b\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327886488-e57cc122-cd4b-4133-94c7-7a58e73f20df.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"222px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 739.5px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"58991375440dbcb4ac71284d7659099e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"423d93fb8719883d8c2f1fa2cd85219c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">三号看板</code> 是有下属内容的，这个看板视图里之所以没有显示出来，是因为 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">三号看板</code> 这个节点也被设置成了看板。点击 <code style=\"font-family: monospace; font-size: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06); padding: 0px 2px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); border-radius: 2px; line-height: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0px;\">三号看板</code> 聚焦到这个节点，就可以看到三号看板内部的内容，依然是一个看板：</p><p data-lake-id=\"3dde03cced19638e22d2e20989ec367f\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"e263777ce884c197a22a9dd48c4361b0\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" class=\"lake-card-margin-top lake-card-margin-bottom\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/995602/1597327926937-656df0cc-3c59-4edf-99cf-b8e8e29d4922.png\" data-raw-src=\"\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" alt=\"image.png\" title=\"image.png\" data-height=\"181px\" style=\"visibility: visible; width: 755px;\"></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"0022a22978770a6b2fde5286bc612f89\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"97e9efc958b5684ae9873fd4331cbf00\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">正如前面所说，整个 workflowy 中的任何一个节点都可以转换为看板，只要该节点没有处于另一个看板视图的内部，就能够以看板视图展示出来。这就是 fractal boards 这个名字的含义，<strong>分形看板可以无限嵌套</strong>，而且还不需要费心去组织管理各个看板，因为 workflowy 的内容组织功能和搜索功能早就很完善了。</p><p data-lake-id=\"509e9cc9aa074d22958e4fae59b3c41d\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"1be1f1c7aacfe4984373942b92b1ec42\" id=\"726Mi\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">与大纲类工具的比较</h2><p data-lake-id=\"0d0f1f1e7ded23f75b145f491ad6386e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"b74e86775862038a4ff7b632b2c26a9e\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">有了分形看板之后，workflowy 瞬间就与一众模仿者拉开了差距。</p><p data-lake-id=\"fb0a68d079ef3b43471d8592c0265193\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"9095086ca2d1fd5c3f4e22c029434599\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">分形看板不仅仅是换了一种视觉展示方式，它还为原本的 workflowy 增加了一套看板式交互方式，以及新的使用策略。</p><p data-lake-id=\"c02da79dd3737ead90816d9199cbc7dc\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"181a1c6f36ca40cb90a05d04f1c42f4c\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">而幕布的思维导图仅仅是把拓扑等价的东西平铺开，生成一个特别不方便观看的长图片，对交互和使用策略没有任何增强。</p><p data-lake-id=\"a14630d621764fbfd82ea6e3b233dd94\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"d32c28b413418589fddd48759e56f2ca\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">以前我说作为大纲软件的 workflowy 是 org-mode 的真子集，现在 workflowy 已经自己开辟出全新的道路了。</p><p data-lake-id=\"e4b49b92b4d73423d7a6a260f3ad2f29\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"a13b8197f9a4f001e7961f62f5b0ebde\" id=\"lh1sB\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">与其它看板工具的比较</h2><p data-lake-id=\"991cc3b1faed926ab6b0db48fa81e06b\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"c90ce31716ee4aea043bdd14dd87fa90\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">现在具有看板功能的工具很多，但是 workflowy 是目前唯一能做到多看板平铺以及完美结合大纲与看板的工具，植根于 workflowy 的分形看板极度流畅，而且可以用大纲方式来编写，在多看板联动上，分形看板毫无疑问是最方便的，所以 workflowy 在看板这个细分领域完全可以抢下一席之地。</p><p data-lake-id=\"bca15d787b2ff5cc3ece71795a3316a6\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"2a1507255957f880b2b9b146ee02565d\" id=\"WjLKz\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">trello 等传统看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"d116f77c7b1446b0d7a57926f56f0592\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"2a363d9523ce9136d4bba06a7ec47884\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"55ecaf4172c050a1edb204bec36306eb\">优势：比起 trello 这样的传统看板，分形看板的最大优势就是可以平铺多个看板，而且可以跨看板直接拖拽任何元素</li><li data-lake-id=\"54775e7f89dc41658e21bf88222c406e\">劣势：workflowy 没有任何富文本特性；trello 有一大堆乱七八糟的功能，仅从看板这个维度来说，trello 的功能要丰富得多</li></ul><h2 data-lake-id=\"2d0a6a6aaeafc38e32bab97f504dc063\" id=\"zvTUQ\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">桌面版滴答清单的看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"657f92769a30549483a1bb171c1a5f21\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"eb2cb5eb0242bf5d06055067c37839a5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\">从任务管理和时间管理的角度来比较：</p><p data-lake-id=\"21de8280495647b1606c7424dcd4030a\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"378390cfcbbd5af9f46aaa814468fdf5\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"2a65a7d2ac9e5270dc0a62898ec07060\">优势：滴答清单的看板模式只是提供了一种新的视图来组织任务，它依然没有实现无限层级子任务，而分形看板里可以添加无限层级的子任务</li><li data-lake-id=\"31dfb560e1470b3d458a2e91920c2e80\">劣势：清单软件可以设置精确到分钟的强制提醒和周期提醒，workflowy 没有强提醒功能</li></ul><h2 data-lake-id=\"15b6a5994aab2242f4936f6cd18ca16c\" id=\"9XMZq\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">notion</h2><p data-lake-id=\"50c40190d3db906ef927fc4a643561cd\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul data-lake-id=\"6f73e2e4f83a69d85663b2193f194d61\" lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li data-lake-id=\"1a1ee2d727f2423bb95a0be235ebb45f\">优势：notion 的 database 打开比较慢，分形看板的各种操作要流畅得多，并且分形看板可以直接跨看板拖拽任意元素</li><li data-lake-id=\"30a7566edae65f2275de773b18a58b92\">劣势：综合来说，如果仅仅比较看板的话，notion 的 database 功能更全更强</li></ul><h2 data-lake-id=\"e479c45b3497361e0c06d81d64ee4a81\" id=\"KmJlj\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">体验分形看板</h2><p data-lake-id=\"ad743133e236f348e55cf24d7dde64c5\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"bookmarklink\" id=\"L5gsg\"><a href=\"https://workflowy.com/invite/723fe6c3.lnx\" style=\"\n    word-wrap: break-word;\n    color: #096DD9;\n    touch-action: manipulation;\n    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0);\n    text-decoration: none;\n    outline: none;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition: color .3s;\n  \">https://workflowy.com/invite/723fe6c3.lnx</a></div></div>",
